    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, budget-friendly option for anyone seeking a dependable daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are solid and perform as expected for its age, providing a smooth ride for your daily commute. The exterior shows its age with some visible scratches and minor fading in the paint, while the interior has sustained some wear and tear on the upholstery. Despite these cosmetic flaws, the car has been regularly serviced and is ready for the road without any immediate mechanical needs.",
